    {
      "type": "frame",
      "id": "HQLZX",
      "x": 0,
      "y": 1922,
      "name": "01 极简 Light",
      "clip": true,
      "width": 375,
      "fill": "#FFFFFF",
      "layout": "vertical",
      "children": [
        {
          "type": "frame",
          "id": "MriVj",
          "name": "hero",
          "metadata": {
            "type": "unsplash",
            "username": "shahabya",
            "link": "https://unsplash.com/@shahabya",
            "author": "shahab yazdi"
          },
          "clip": true,
          "width": "fill_container",
          "height": 220,
          "fill": {
            "type": "image",
            "enabled": true,
            "url": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1571558225867-e4a256347652?crop=entropy&cs=tinysrgb&fit=max&fm=jpg&ixid=M3w4NDM0ODN8MHwxfHJhbmRvbXx8fHx8fHx8fDE3NzI1Nzk4MTJ8&ixlib=rb-4.1.0&q=80&w=1080",
            "mode": "fill"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "frame",
          "id": "4B6UK",
          "name": "contentWrap",
          "width": "fill_container",
          "layout": "vertical",
          "gap": 20,
          "padding": 24,
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "rJIuF",
              "name": "articleTitle",
              "fill": "#164E63",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "content": "设计的本质：少即是多",
              "lineHeight": 1.3,
              "fontFamily": "Archivo",
              "fontSize": 28,
              "fontWeight": "700"
            },
            {
              "type": "frame",
              "id": "dRWAr",
              "name": "metaRow",
              "gap": 8,
              "alignItems": "center",
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "ellipse",
                  "id": "PJV3Q",
                  "name": "avatar1",
                  "fill": "#0891B2",
                  "width": 24,
                  "height": 24
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "OsiF3",
                  "name": "authorName",
                  "fill": "#334155",
                  "content": "林清远",
                  "fontFamily": "Space Grotesk",
                  "fontSize": 13,
                  "fontWeight": "500"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "joYfT",
                  "name": "dateDot",
                  "fill": "#94A3B8",
                  "content": "·",
                  "fontFamily": "Space Grotesk",
                  "fontSize": 13,
                  "fontWeight": "normal"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "X59zp",
                  "name": "dateText",
                  "fill": "#94A3B8",
                  "content": "2026.03.04",
                  "fontFamily": "Space Grotesk",
                  "fontSize": 13,
                  "fontWeight": "normal"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "rectangle",
              "id": "WIOci",
              "name": "divider1",
              "fill": "#E2E8F0",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "height": 1
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "4Beh6",
              "name": "intro",
              "fill": "#334155",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "content": "在信息过载的时代，真正打动人心的设计往往是最简洁的。从包豪斯到当代数字界面，极简主义始终是设计师追求的终极美学。",
              "lineHeight": 1.8,
              "fontFamily": "Space Grotesk",
              "fontSize": 15,
              "fontWeight": "normal"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "ocGzq",
              "name": "h2a",
              "fill": "#164E63",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "content": "一、留白的力量",
              "fontFamily": "Archivo",
              "fontSize": 20,
              "fontWeight": "700"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "ysozD",
              "name": "bodyA",
              "fill": "#334155",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "content": "留白不是空虚，而是呼吸的空间。日本传统美学中的「間」——空间与停顿的艺术，深刻影响了现代极简设计。苹果的产品页面、无印良品的包装，都在用大量留白传递一种从容与克制。设计师原研哉曾说：「白是一种可能性，而非空无。」",
              "lineHeight": 1.8,
              "fontFamily": "Space Grotesk",
              "fontSize": 15,
              "fontWeight": "normal"
            },
            {
              "type": "frame",
              "id": "6LHRV",
              "name": "pullQuote",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "gap": 12,
              "padding": [
                16,
                0,
                16,
                16
              ],
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "rectangle",
                  "cornerRadius": 2,
                  "id": "1lDum",
                  "name": "accentBar",
                  "fill": "#0891B2",
                  "width": 3,
                  "height": "fill_container"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "eP3OC",
                  "name": "quoteText",
                  "fill": "#0891B2",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "「少即是多，不是减少内容，而是提炼本质。」\n—— 密斯·凡·德·罗",
                  "lineHeight": 1.7,
                  "fontFamily": "Space Grotesk",
                  "fontSize": 14,
                  "fontWeight": "normal",
                  "fontStyle": "italic"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "frame",
              "id": "8Xs4L",
              "name": "articleImage",
              "metadata": {
                "type": "unsplash",
                "username": "budkoolga",
                "link": "https://unsplash.com/@budkoolga",
                "author": "Olga Budko"
              },
              "clip": true,
              "width": "fill_container",
              "height": 200,
              "fill": {
                "type": "image",
                "enabled": true,
                "url": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1610571181717-fd5f7645888b?crop=entropy&cs=tinysrgb&fit=max&fm=jpg&ixid=M3w4NDM0ODN8MHwxfHJhbmRvbXx8fHx8fHx8fDE3NzI1Nzk4Mjl8&ixlib=rb-4.1.0&q=80&w=1080",
                "mode": "fill"
              },
              "cornerRadius": 12
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "K5KLH",
              "name": "h2b",
              "fill": "#164E63",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "content": "二、色彩的减法",
              "fontFamily": "Archivo",
              "fontSize": 20,
              "fontWeight": "700"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "3ggjE",
              "name": "bodyB",
              "fill": "#334155",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "content": "极简设计中，色彩不是越多越好。一个主色、一个辅色、加上黑白灰的基底，就足以构建层次丰富的视觉体系。过多的色彩会分散注意力，而克制的用色能让每一抹颜色都更加有力。Dieter Rams 为博朗设计的产品，常常只用一两种颜色，却经久不衰。",
              "lineHeight": 1.8,
              "fontFamily": "Space Grotesk",
              "fontSize": 15,
              "fontWeight": "normal"
            },
            {
              "type": "frame",
              "id": "JUsSL",
              "name": "tipBox",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "fill": "#ECFEFF",
              "cornerRadius": 12,
              "layout": "vertical",
              "gap": 8,
              "padding": 16,
