                  "fill": "#334155",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "试试在你的下一个项目中，先做减法：去掉所有装饰性元素，只保留传达信息必需的部分，然后观察设计是否变得更好。",
                  "lineHeight": 1.7,
                  "fontFamily": "Space Grotesk",
                  "fontSize": 14,
                  "fontWeight": "normal"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "o03Rm",
              "name": "h2c",
              "fill": "#164E63",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "content": "三、功能即美学",
              "fontFamily": "Archivo",
              "fontSize": 20,
              "fontWeight": "700"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "XMvCK",
              "name": "bodyC",
              "fill": "#334155",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "content": "极简主义的核心理念是：每一个元素都必须服务于功能。没有纯粹的装饰，没有多余的线条。这种设计哲学与中国传统的「大道至简」不谋而合。最好的设计，是让用户感受不到设计的存在——一切都如此自然、流畅、不言自明。",
              "lineHeight": 1.8,
              "fontFamily": "Space Grotesk",
              "fontSize": 15,
              "fontWeight": "normal"
            },
