                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "rectangle",
              "id": "ntwMT",
              "name": "divider1",
              "fill": "#1E293B",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "height": 1
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "kk3x9",
              "name": "intro",
              "fill": "#CBD5E1",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "content": "在信息过载的时代，真正打动人心的设计往往是最简洁的。从包豪斯到当代数字界面，极简主义始终是设计师追求的终极美学。",
              "lineHeight": 1.8,
              "fontFamily": "Space Grotesk",
              "fontSize": 15,
              "fontWeight": "normal"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "W8bmd",
              "name": "h2a",
              "fill": "#E0F7FA",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "content": "一、留白的力量",
              "fontFamily": "Archivo",
              "fontSize": 20,
              "fontWeight": "700"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "jeZO9",
              "name": "bodyA",
              "fill": "#CBD5E1",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "content": "留白不是空虚，而是呼吸的空间。日本传统美学中的「間」——空间与停顿的艺术，深刻影响了现代极简设计。苹果的产品页面、无印良品的包装，都在用大量留白传递一种从容与克制。设计师原研哉曾说：「白是一种可能性，而非空无。」",
              "lineHeight": 1.8,
              "fontFamily": "Space Grotesk",
              "fontSize": 15,
              "fontWeight": "normal"
            },
            {
              "type": "frame",
              "id": "PMcoA",
              "name": "pullQuote",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "gap": 12,
              "padding": [
                16,
                0,
                16,
                16
              ],
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "rectangle",
                  "cornerRadius": 2,
                  "id": "MiKob",
                  "name": "accentBar",
                  "fill": "#22D3EE",
                  "width": 3,
                  "height": "fill_container"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "1vbw1",
                  "name": "quoteText",
                  "fill": "#22D3EE",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "「少即是多，不是减少内容，而是提炼本质。」\n—— 密斯·凡·德·罗",
                  "lineHeight": 1.7,
                  "fontFamily": "Space Grotesk",
                  "fontSize": 14,
                  "fontWeight": "normal",
                  "fontStyle": "italic"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "frame",
              "id": "8Nxsi",
              "name": "articleImage",
              "metadata": {
                "type": "unsplash",
                "username": "budkoolga",
                "link": "https://unsplash.com/@budkoolga",
                "author": "Olga Budko"
