              "clip": true,
              "width": "fill_container",
              "height": 200,
              "fill": {
                "type": "image",
                "enabled": true,
                "url": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1610571181717-fd5f7645888b?crop=entropy&cs=tinysrgb&fit=max&fm=jpg&ixid=M3w4NDM0ODN8MHwxfHJhbmRvbXx8fHx8fHx8fDE3NzI1Nzk4Mjl8&ixlib=rb-4.1.0&q=80&w=1080",
                "mode": "fill"
              },
              "cornerRadius": 12
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "T7MR4",
              "name": "h2b",
              "fill": "#E0F7FA",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "content": "二、色彩的减法",
              "fontFamily": "Archivo",
              "fontSize": 20,
              "fontWeight": "700"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "UBpUx",
              "name": "bodyB",
              "fill": "#CBD5E1",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "content": "极简设计中，色彩不是越多越好。一个主色、一个辅色、加上黑白灰的基底，就足以构建层次丰富的视觉体系。过多的色彩会分散注意力，而克制的用色能让每一抹颜色都更加有力。Dieter Rams 为博朗设计的产品，常常只用一两种颜色，却经久不衰。",
              "lineHeight": 1.8,
              "fontFamily": "Space Grotesk",
              "fontSize": 15,
              "fontWeight": "normal"
            },
