            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "6jVyk",
              "name": "intro2",
              "fill": "#3F3F46",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "content": "从古登堡到数字时代，排版术经历了六百年的演变。在每一次技术革命的浪潮中，排版始终是连接思想与读者的桥梁。",
              "lineHeight": 1.8,
              "fontFamily": "Public Sans",
              "fontSize": 15,
              "fontWeight": "normal"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "Vknpq",
              "name": "h2a2",
              "fill": "#09090B",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "content": "一、铅字的温度",
              "fontFamily": "Libre Bodoni",
              "fontSize": 20,
              "fontWeight": "700"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "z06aj",
              "name": "bodyA2",
              "fill": "#3F3F46",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "content": "活字印刷术的诞生改变了人类文明的传播方式。每一颗铅字都经过铸造、打磨，带着手工的温度。Garamond、Caslon、Baskerville——这些经典字体的名字背后，是数百年排版匠人对完美比例的不懈追求。在数字化大潮中，我们是否遗失了那份对字形的敬畏？",
              "lineHeight": 1.8,
              "fontFamily": "Public Sans",
              "fontSize": 15,
              "fontWeight": "normal"
            },
            {
              "type": "frame",
              "id": "Z40IH",
              "name": "pullQuote2",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "layout": "vertical",
              "gap": 8,
              "padding": [
                20,
                24
              ],
              "alignItems": "center",
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "rectangle",
                  "id": "JlNme",
                  "name": "pqTopLine",
                  "fill": "#EC4899",
                  "width": 40,
                  "height": 2
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "NIPL9",
                  "name": "pqText2",
                  "fill": "#09090B",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "「排版不是装饰，\n而是语言的视觉形态。」",
                  "lineHeight": 1.6,
                  "textAlign": "center",
                  "fontFamily": "Libre Bodoni",
                  "fontSize": 18,
                  "fontWeight": "normal",
                  "fontStyle": "italic"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "UUzTD",
                  "name": "pqAttr",
                  "fill": "#A1A1AA",
                  "content": "—— Jan Tschichold",
