              "height": 200,
              "fill": {
                "type": "image",
                "enabled": true,
                "url": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1635621456241-16e4a3a009a0?crop=entropy&cs=tinysrgb&fit=max&fm=jpg&ixid=M3w4NDM0ODN8MHwxfHJhbmRvbXx8fHx8fHx8fDE3NzI1Nzk5NjJ8&ixlib=rb-4.1.0&q=80&w=1080",
                "mode": "fill"
              }
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "Yh7yW",
              "name": "h2b2",
              "fill": "#09090B",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "content": "二、网格的秩序",
              "fontFamily": "Libre Bodoni",
              "fontSize": 20,
              "fontWeight": "700"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "WbSIX",
              "name": "bodyB2",
              "fill": "#3F3F46",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "content": "瑞士国际主义风格将网格系统推向了极致。Josef Müller-Brockmann 的作品证明，严谨的网格不是束缚，而是自由的基石。每一条基线、每一个栏宽都经过精密计算。当所有元素都找到自己的位置，设计便拥有了秩序之美，读者的眼睛也有了清晰的路径。",
              "lineHeight": 1.8,
              "fontFamily": "Public Sans",
              "fontSize": 15,
              "fontWeight": "normal"
            },
            {
              "type": "frame",
              "id": "AYAF4",
              "name": "tipBox2",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "fill": "#FDF2F8",
              "stroke": {
                "align": "inside",
                "thickness": 1,
                "fill": "#FBCFE8"
              },
              "gap": 12,
              "padding": 16,
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "rectangle",
                  "id": "Vsc3u",
                  "name": "tipBar2",
                  "fill": "#EC4899",
                  "width": 3,
                  "height": "fill_container"
                },
                {
                  "type": "frame",
                  "id": "YL7nR",
                  "name": "tipContent2",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "layout": "vertical",
                  "gap": 6,
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "zwWDu",
                      "name": "tipLabel2",
                      "fill": "#EC4899",
                      "content": "排版要点",
                      "fontFamily": "Libre Bodoni",
                      "fontSize": 13,
                      "fontWeight": "700"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "64Y6F",
                      "name": "tipBody2",
                      "fill": "#3F3F46",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "优秀的排版需要关注行距、字距和段距的协调。理想的行长为 45-75 个字符，行距通常为字号的 1.4-1.8 倍。",
                      "lineHeight": 1.7,
                      "fontFamily": "Public Sans",
                      "fontSize": 14,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "2Ysmd",
              "name": "h2c2",
              "fill": "#09090B",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "content": "三、数字时代的新篇章",
              "fontFamily": "Libre Bodoni",
              "fontSize": 20,
              "fontWeight": "700"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "Y5ag6",
              "name": "bodyC2",
              "fill": "#3F3F46",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "content": "Web 字体、可变字体、响应式排版——技术的进步为排版带来了前所未有的可能性。但核心原则始终未变：清晰、可读、优美。在屏幕阅读成为主流的今天，排版的重要性不是降低了，而是更加凸显。每一个像素都承载着对读者的尊重。",
              "lineHeight": 1.8,
              "fontFamily": "Public Sans",
              "fontSize": 15,
              "fontWeight": "normal"
            },
