            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "U3FBl",
              "name": "intro4D",
              "fill": "#94A3B8",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "content": "当 AI 从代码补全进化到自主编程，开发者的角色正在被重新定义。这不仅是工具的升级，更是一场关于创造力与效率的革命。",
              "lineHeight": 1.8,
              "fontFamily": "DM Sans",
              "fontSize": 15,
              "fontWeight": "normal"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "6lFSy",
              "name": "h2aD",
              "fill": "#F8FAFC",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "content": "一、从代码补全到代码生成",
              "lineHeight": 1.4,
              "fontFamily": "Space Grotesk",
              "fontSize": 20,
              "fontWeight": "700"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "FdR5S",
              "name": "bodyAD",
              "fill": "#94A3B8",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "content": "早期的 AI 编程工具只能提供简单的代码补全，但如今的大语言模型已经能够理解完整的项目上下文，生成复杂的代码逻辑。从 GitHub Copilot 到 Claude Code，工具的能力边界正在不断扩展。开发者不再需要逐行编写每一段代码，而是转向更高层次的架构设计和逻辑规划。",
              "lineHeight": 1.8,
              "fontFamily": "DM Sans",
              "fontSize": 15,
              "fontWeight": "normal"
            },
            {
              "type": "frame",
              "id": "Y0hdx",
              "name": "pullQuote4D",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "fill": "#1E293B",
              "stroke": {
                "align": "inside",
                "thickness": {
                  "left": 3
                },
                "fill": "#22C55E"
              },
              "gap": 12,
              "padding": [
                16,
                20
              ],
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "8DgQo",
                  "name": "quoteTextD",
                  "fill": "#F8FAFC",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "「未来的程序员不是写代码的人，而是指导 AI 写代码的人。」",
                  "lineHeight": 1.7,
                  "fontFamily": "Space Grotesk",
                  "fontSize": 15,
                  "fontWeight": "500",
                  "fontStyle": "italic"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "frame",
              "id": "u4kTs",
