              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "rectangle",
              "id": "6Fyzq",
              "name": "divider7a",
              "fill": "#020617",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "height": 3
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "94IqZ",
              "name": "intro7",
              "fill": "#334155",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "content": "在设计的世界里，规则是用来被打破的。当所有人都在追求圆润、柔和、友好的设计语言时，一股粗犷的力量正在悄然崛起。它拒绝修饰，拥抱原始，用最直接的方式冲击你的视觉神经。",
              "lineHeight": 1.8,
              "fontFamily": "Public Sans",
              "fontSize": 15,
              "fontWeight": "normal"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "hWHKZ",
              "name": "h2text7a",
              "fill": "#020617",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "content": "野蛮生长的美学",
              "lineHeight": 1.3,
              "fontFamily": "Lexend Mega",
              "fontSize": 20,
              "fontWeight": "800"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "WqvfB",
              "name": "body7a",
              "fill": "#334155",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "content": "Brutalism——这个源自建筑领域的概念正在数字设计中掀起一场革命。它崇尚材料的真实性，拒绝一切不必要的装饰。在网页设计中，这意味着大胆的排版、粗重的线条、高对比度的配色和毫不掩饰的网格结构。\n\n这不是懒惰，而是一种刻意的选择——用最少的元素传达最强的信息。",
              "lineHeight": 1.8,
              "fontFamily": "Public Sans",
              "fontSize": 15,
              "fontWeight": "normal"
            },
            {
              "type": "frame",
              "id": "IY04K",
              "name": "quote7",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "fill": "#020617",
              "layout": "vertical",
              "gap": 8,
              "padding": 20,
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "31CfN",
                  "name": "quoteText7",
                  "fill": "#F8FAFC",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "GOOD DESIGN IS AS LITTLE DESIGN AS POSSIBLE.",
                  "lineHeight": 1.5,
                  "fontFamily": "Lexend Mega",
                  "fontSize": 15,
                  "fontWeight": "700"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "peH9g",
                  "name": "quoteAuthor7",
                  "fill": "#94A3B8",
                  "content": "— DIETER RAMS",
                  "fontFamily": "Public Sans",
                  "fontSize": 12,
                  "fontWeight": "700"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "frame",
              "id": "v5Wby",
              "name": "artImg7",
              "metadata": {
                "type": "unsplash",
                "username": "rebecca_h",
                "link": "https://unsplash.com/@rebecca_h",
                "author": "Rebecca Hausner"
              },
              "clip": true,
              "width": "fill_container",
              "height": 200,
              "fill": {
                "type": "image",
                "enabled": true,
                "url": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1699359104595-99d9165579ea?crop=entropy&cs=tinysrgb&fit=max&fm=jpg&ixid=M3w4NDM0ODN8MHwxfHJhbmRvbXx8fHx8fHx8fDE3NzI5NjUwNzd8&ixlib=rb-4.1.0&q=80&w=1080",
                "mode": "fill"
              },
              "stroke": {
                "align": "inside",
                "thickness": 3,
                "fill": "#020617"
              }
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "lfuaG",
              "name": "h2text7b",
              "fill": "#020617",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "content": "解构与重建",
              "lineHeight": 1.3,
              "fontFamily": "Lexend Mega",
              "fontSize": 20,
              "fontWeight": "800"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "8KSuQ",
              "name": "body7b",
              "fill": "#334155",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "content": "当我们谈论粗犷主义设计时，不仅仅是在讨论一种视觉风格。它更是一种态度——对过度精致化的反思，对功能至上的回归。每一条粗线、每一个锐角都在宣告：内容才是王道。\n\n从 Craigslist 到早期的 Bloomberg 网站，这些「丑陋」的设计却拥有着惊人的使用效率。",
              "lineHeight": 1.8,
              "fontFamily": "Public Sans",
              "fontSize": 15,
              "fontWeight": "normal"
            },
            {
              "type": "frame",
              "id": "W9lpH",
              "name": "tipBox7",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "fill": "#F8FAFC",
              "stroke": {
                "thickness": 3,
                "fill": "#020617"
              },
              "layout": "vertical",
              "gap": 12,
              "padding": 20,
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "4qC3t",
                  "name": "tipTitle7",
                  "fill": "#0369A1",
                  "content": "BRUTALIST PRINCIPLES",
                  "fontFamily": "Lexend Mega",
                  "fontSize": 14,
                  "fontWeight": "800"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "fuuYx",
                  "name": "tipItem7a",
                  "fill": "#334155",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "// 功能优先，拒绝无意义的装饰",
                  "lineHeight": 1.7,
                  "fontFamily": "Public Sans",
                  "fontSize": 14,
                  "fontWeight": "normal"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "OiMd2",
                  "name": "tipItem7b",
                  "fill": "#334155",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "// 拥抱不完美，展示真实的材料质感",
                  "lineHeight": 1.7,
                  "fontFamily": "Public Sans",
                  "fontSize": 14,
                  "fontWeight": "normal"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "sU5JX",
                  "name": "tipItem7c",
                  "fill": "#334155",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "// 高对比度，让信息层次一目了然",
                  "lineHeight": 1.7,
                  "fontFamily": "Public Sans",
                  "fontSize": 14,
                  "fontWeight": "normal"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "RT0hN",
              "name": "h2text7c",
              "fill": "#020617",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "content": "回归本质",
              "lineHeight": 1.3,
              "fontFamily": "Lexend Mega",
              "fontSize": 20,
              "fontWeight": "800"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "jjV2k",
              "name": "body7c",
              "fill": "#334155",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "content": "粗犷不是粗糙，反叛不是叛逆。在信息爆炸的时代，粗犷主义设计提醒我们回归设计的本质：有效地传递信息。当你剥去所有的虚饰，留下的就是最纯粹的力量。",
              "lineHeight": 1.8,
              "fontFamily": "Public Sans",
              "fontSize": 15,
              "fontWeight": "normal"
            },
