                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "d3Ezo",
              "name": "intro8",
              "fill": "#A5B4FC",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "content": "灵感就像一只调皮的小猫，你越追它，它越跑。但如果你创造了合适的环境，它就会自己跱到你身边来。让我们一起探索如何让创意思维成为你的日常伙伴！",
              "lineHeight": 1.8,
              "fontFamily": "Nunito",
              "fontSize": 15,
              "fontWeight": "normal"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "bo7fI",
              "name": "h2text8a",
              "fill": "#E0E7FF",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "content": "🎨 打开感官的天线",
              "lineHeight": 1.4,
              "fontFamily": "Fredoka",
              "fontSize": 21,
              "fontWeight": "700"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "KMxx5",
              "name": "body8a",
              "fill": "#A5B4FC",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "content": "创意不是凭空而来的，它需要你的感官时刻保持开放。试试看：下次喝咖啡时，闭上眼睛感受味道的层次；散步时，注意观察光影的变化；听音乐时，尝试去分辨每一种乐器的声音。\n\n这些看似微小的练习，却能让你的大脑建立更多的神经连接，为创意的迨发打下基础。",
              "lineHeight": 1.8,
              "fontFamily": "Nunito",
              "fontSize": 15,
              "fontWeight": "normal"
            },
            {
              "type": "frame",
              "id": "uC4f8",
              "name": "quote8",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "fill": "#2D2A5E",
              "cornerRadius": 20,
              "stroke": {
                "thickness": 3,
                "fill": "#818CF8"
              },
              "effect": [
                {
                  "type": "shadow",
                  "shadowType": "outer",
