              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "rectangle",
              "id": "4jIfS",
              "name": "divider9",
              "fill": "#1E293B",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "height": 1
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "x6rt4",
              "name": "intro9",
              "fill": "#CBD5E1",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "content": "在当今快速变化的商业环境中，数字化转型已成为企业保持竞争力的必要手段。然而，根据麦肯锡的最新研究，超过70%的数字化转型项目未能达到预期目标。本文将深入分析成功企业的转型经验，为您提供五个经过验证的关键策略。",
              "lineHeight": 1.8,
              "fontFamily": "Open Sans",
              "fontSize": 15,
              "fontWeight": "normal"
            },
            {
              "type": "frame",
              "id": "FmmeW",
              "name": "h2row1",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "gap": 12,
              "alignItems": "center",
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "rectangle",
                  "cornerRadius": 2,
                  "id": "gB7Bf",
                  "name": "h2bar1",
                  "fill": "#60A5FA",
                  "width": 4,
                  "height": 24
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "63IyA",
                  "name": "h2text1",
                  "fill": "#F8FAFC",
                  "content": "策略一：以客户为中心的战略重塑",
                  "lineHeight": 1.4,
                  "fontFamily": "Poppins",
                  "fontSize": 20,
                  "fontWeight": "700"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "X4sfr",
              "name": "body1",
              "fill": "#CBD5E1",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "content": "成功的数字化转型始于对客户需求的深刻理解。企业需要重新审视价值链的每一个环节，将传统的产品导向思维转变为客户体验导向。通过数据驱动的客户洞察，企业可以精准识别客户痛点，提供个性化的解决方案。",
              "lineHeight": 1.8,
              "fontFamily": "Open Sans",
              "fontSize": 15,
              "fontWeight": "normal"
            },
            {
              "type": "frame",
              "id": "KDgqf",
              "name": "quote9",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "gap": 16,
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "rectangle",
                  "cornerRadius": 2,
                  "id": "xDfgi",
                  "name": "quoteBar9",
                  "fill": "#EAB308",
                  "width": 3,
                  "height": 100
                },
                {
                  "type": "frame",
                  "id": "GobaZ",
                  "name": "quoteInner9",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "layout": "vertical",
                  "gap": 10,
                  "padding": [
                    8,
                    0
                  ],
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "Hu67d",
                      "name": "quoteText9",
                      "fill": "#60A5FA",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "&quot;数字化不是简单的技术升级，而是一场以客户为中心的商业模式变革。成功的企业将技术视为赋能工具，而非目的本身。&quot;",
                      "lineHeight": 1.7,
                      "fontFamily": "Open Sans",
                      "fontSize": 14,
                      "fontWeight": "500",
                      "fontStyle": "italic"
                    },
