            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "zHKkT",
              "name": "intro10",
              "fill": "#D4D4D8",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "content": "在数字化浪潮席卷全球的今天，艺术与技术的边界正在被重新定义。从AI生成艺术到沉浸式交互装置，创作者们正在用代码书写新的美学宣言。本文将探索这场跨越维度的创意革命。",
              "lineHeight": 1.8,
              "fontFamily": "Manrope",
              "fontSize": 15,
              "fontWeight": "normal"
            },
            {
              "type": "frame",
              "id": "7K4Hy",
              "name": "sec1header10",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "gap": 12,
              "alignItems": "center",
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "FXrdX",
                  "name": "sec1num",
                  "fill": "#F472B6",
                  "content": "01",
                  "fontFamily": "Syne",
                  "fontSize": 32,
                  "fontWeight": "800"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "ip1CR",
                  "name": "sec1title",
                  "fill": "#FAFAFA",
                  "content": "数字艺术的新纪元",
                  "lineHeight": 1.3,
                  "fontFamily": "Syne",
                  "fontSize": 20,
                  "fontWeight": "700"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "yohCf",
              "name": "body10a",
              "fill": "#D4D4D8",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "content": "当算法开始创造美，当像素成为画布，数字艺术正在经历一场前所未有的革命。从Beeple的NFT作品以6930万美元成交，到Refik Anadol用数据雕塑重新定义公共艺术，我们正站在一个全新创作时代的起点。",
              "lineHeight": 1.8,
              "fontFamily": "Manrope",
              "fontSize": 15,
              "fontWeight": "normal"
            },
            {
              "type": "frame",
              "id": "pVM34",
              "name": "quote10",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "fill": "#27272A",
              "layout": "vertical",
              "gap": 12,
              "padding": [
                20,
                24
              ],
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "YESME",
                  "name": "quoteMarker",
                  "fill": "#F472B6",
                  "content": "//",
                  "fontFamily": "Syne",
                  "fontSize": 28,
                  "fontWeight": "800"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "073Uy",
                  "name": "quoteText10",
                  "fill": "#D4D4D8",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "艺术不是对现实的逃避，而是对现实的深入。当技术成为我们的延伸，创造力便获得了新的自由。",
                  "lineHeight": 1.7,
                  "fontFamily": "Manrope",
                  "fontSize": 14,
                  "fontWeight": "500",
                  "fontStyle": "italic"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "iRJGw",
                  "name": "quoteAuthor10",
                  "fill": "#A1A1AA",
                  "content": "— Refik Anadol",
                  "fontFamily": "Manrope",
                  "fontSize": 12,
                  "fontWeight": "normal"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "frame",
              "id": "ohehs",
              "name": "articleImg10",
              "metadata": {
                "type": "unsplash",
                "username": "avivarma",
                "link": "https://unsplash.com/@avivarma",
                "author": "Avi Varma"
              },
              "clip": true,
